01) Elephant is bigger than the dog
bigger_than(elephant,dog).

02) Elephant is bigger than the dog (alternative)
bigger(elephant,dog).

03) Monkey eats banana
eats(monkey,banana).

04) John likes Ann
likes(john,ann).

05) Charlie studies AI
studies(charlie,ai).

06) Collins teaches CS
teaches(collins,cs).

07) Vincent loves Mia
loves(vincent,mia).

08) September comes after October
next_month(september,october).

09) Jane is a student of Roy
is_a_student_of(jane,roy).

10) Elephant is black
color_is(elephant,black).


