EXERCISE
---------

1) Tom is a parent of Bob
parent(tom,bob).

2) Pam is a parent of Bob
parent(pam,bob).

3) Tom is a parent of Liz
parent(tom,liz).

4) Bob is a parent of Ann
parent(bob,ann).

5) Bob is a parent of Pat
parent(bob,pat).

6) Pat is a parent of Jim
parent(pat,jim).


Queries
--------
1) Is Bob a parent of Tom?
parent(bob,tom).

2) Is Tom parent of Jim?
parent(tom,jim).

3) Is Ann child of Bob?
parent(bob,ann).

